<html>

<head>
  <meta charset='utf-8' />
  <title>Test payment checkout</title>
  <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <meta name="robots" content="noindex, nofollow" />

  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      display: flex;
      width: 100vw;
      height: 100vh;
      background: #bbb;
    }

    .card {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      max-width: 32rem;
      margin: auto;
      padding: 2rem;
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 0.5rem;
    }

    form {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 1rem;
      width: 100%;
      margin-top: 2rem;
    }

    h1 {
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    p {
      text-align: center;
    }

    .radio {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: .5rem;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    .status {
      display: flex;
      gap: 1rem;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    input[type=submit] {
      flex-shrink: 0;
      padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
      border-radius: .25rem;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    input[type=submit]:hover {
      background-color: #bbb;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class='card'>
    <h1>Test payment checkout</h1>
    <p>You can now select the final state of your test payment. The payment status will be sent to your website.</p>
    <form method='post'>
      <input type='hidden' name='redirect_url' value='{{redirect_url}}' />

      <p>Payment status:</p>

      <div class="status">
        <input type='submit' name='status' value='paid' />
        <input type='submit' name='status' value='failed' />
      </div>
    </form>
  </div>
</body>

</html>